thelatest.title: The Latest (StartUp) - Mobile Application Developer and Developer (05-2016 / 07-2016)
thelatest.description: I worked for two months at StartUp The Latest as a developer and developer of mobile application. My main job was to develop an application for the company website. The company was close to launching its final product and I was tasked with developing the application for android system during my period there. It was a great opportunity to learn about the world of StartUps and experience an American business environment.
